, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.56231752647767e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"gender parity\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"Marie Sallois\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"gender equality\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"-Aug\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It took a very long time for us to finally get to 44 per cent (of women) in London in 2012, the first edition at which women could take part in all the sports, then 48 per cent in Tokyo (in 2021).\\\"\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1362, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999988634833336, \"rank\": 1.1272663177340096e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999959053213546, \"rank\": 4.094441195715991e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"44 per cent\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"the first edition\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"all the sports\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The barriers for women were once so high they were forced to compete in a rival \\\"Women's Olympics\\\" in the 1920s.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The barriers\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"a rival\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Women's Olympics\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1928 in Amsterdam, they were allowed to compete in athletics for the first time, but the sight of exhausted female runners after the 800m final appalled male onlookers so much that they were excluded again.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"score\": 0.999999996227416, \"rank\": 3.770159776283607e-09, \"text\": \"Amsterdam\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amsterdam\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"the sight\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"exhausted female runners\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m final appalled male onlookers\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until 1960, women were barred from competing in any race of more than 200m, and even in 1976, women's events made up only a quarter of the Olympic programme.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"any race\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 200m\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"women's events\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"only a quarter\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic programme\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And long considered unable to cope with the physical demands of the marathon, they were finally allowed to take part for the first time at the Los Angeles Games in 1984.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the physical demands\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"the Los Angeles Games\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris Games will not only feature as many women as men, it will also give greater prominence to women's events.\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paris Games\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"as many women\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"greater prominence\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"women's events\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of the men's marathon being the athletics event leading up to the closing ceremony, it will be the women's.\", \"from\": 2